values:
Ummm...I hate to do this, but I don't get a lot of time to read friends pages these days, and when I first got involved here I seemed to have a lot more "active" friends than I do now.

I think I'll give it a week so that perhaps some people will manage to get in if they can, but I'd like you to comment on this post please if you are on my friends list and wish to remain on it.&nbsp;&nbsp; This way I can weed out those that may not be with us in LJ land any more.&nbsp;&nbsp; And conversely, I won't be offended if you'd like to comment and say that you are happy to be removed if you so wish.

These types of posts are pretty shitty to put up, but sometimes they just need doing.&nbsp;
